flowchart TD
    A[App Issue Reported] --> B[Categorize: bug/regression/UX]
    B --> C{Severity}
    C -- P0/P1 --> D[Hotfix Branch]
    C -- P2/P3 --> E[Backlog]
    D --> F[Reproduce + Diagnose]
    F --> G[Apply Fix + Regression Test]
    G --> H[Deploy via CI]
    H --> I[Post-mortem in retrospectives/]
    E --> J[Sprint Planning]
